    "body": "We were unsetting the CFLAGS to get control of Py_LIMITED_API so it wasn't overridden by the global flags. However this also meant that we were losing \"-Og/-O0\" and so it was compiling slower than needed.\r\n\r\nThis adds a way of unsetting only some of the CFLAGS so we can control the Cython-specific stuff without affecting our general CFLAGS.\r\n\r\nOn my laptop, this runs in just under half the time.",
    "closed_at": null,
