                },
                "message": "Speed up isolated_limited test\n\nWe were unsetting the CFLAGS to get control of Py_LIMITED_API\nso it wasn't overridden by the global flags. However this also\nmeant that we were losing \"-Og/-O0\" and so it was compiling slower\nthan needed.\n\nThis adds a way of unsetting only some of the CFLAGS so we can\ncontrol the Cython-specific stuff without affecting our general\nCFLAGS.\n\nOn my laptop, this runs in just under half the time.",
